Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.88,0:00:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That evening I saw my mother in town.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.88,0:00:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She was wearing her priestess garb as always,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.00,0:00:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,walking slowly in the sunset\Nas if she were simply wandering around.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.50,0:00:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The excitement I felt from seeing her\Nafter such a long time rushed out
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.62,0:00:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and before I could question it,\NI just couldn't help talking to her.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.54,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe my mother didn't hear my voice.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.12,0:00:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She kept walking wherever she was heading\Nwithout even looking back.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.04,0:00:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I hurried after my mother and\Nturned the corner right behind her.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.29,0:00:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But... there was no one there.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.96,0:00:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I have the wrong person?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.04,0:00:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It had to be.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.62,0:00:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way my mother\Nwould be here anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.62,0:00:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Because my mother is no longer...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.75,0:01:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right then, as the streetlight flickered,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.58,0:01:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw my mother's back in the\Nblue white fluorescent light.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.04,0:01:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of the rod in her hand echoed
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.50,0:01:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and the faint scent of medicine\Nand sweet herbs hung in the air.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.92,0:01:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the scent of my mother that I remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.50,0:01:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother appeared and disappeared\Nas the light flickered.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.79,0:01:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I followed her, trying to stop her,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.04,0:01:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but every time the light flickered,\Nshe appeared further and further away.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.25,0:01:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was doing my best to catch up,\Nbut I just couldn't.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.33,0:01:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was walking slowly,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.08,0:01:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but every time the light flickered\Nshe appeared further and further away.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.62,0:02:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear that I may not see her again\Ndrove me to scream her name.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.21,0:02:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right then my mother turned towards me.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.58,0:02:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,At that very moment a bright light flashed.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.00,0:02:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That must've triggered the filament to break.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.50,0:02:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The streetlight went out and my mother\Ndisappeared into the darkness.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.96,0:02:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't understand what happened\Nand just stood there.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.54,0:02:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My beloved mother, whom I've so missed,\Nand had been dying to see again,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.12,0:02:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,was now right in front of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.54,0:02:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time I knew it was\Nsimply impossible,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.33,0:02:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,because my mother was no longer...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.92,0:04:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kagami.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.58,0:04:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.17,0:04:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yawn...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.54,0:04:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? It's my precious naptime right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't interrupt.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami, listen to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.58,0:04:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you listen to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.79,0:04:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw my mother yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.79,0:04:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.33,0:04:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.88,0:04:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...I saw my mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.21,0:04:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid or what? Are you dying?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.62,0:04:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to literally give me a break.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.75,0:04:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I don't have time to deal with nonsense like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.92,0:04:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop interrupting my sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.67,0:05:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, Kagami, come shopping\Nwith me after school.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.67,0:05:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.21,0:05:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a bicycle, but have no idea which one I should get.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.83,0:05:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not making any sense right now.\NI'm not following you at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.83,0:05:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go asking my brother\Nto give me a bike ride every day.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Two people are not allowed to ride together anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.62,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.29,0:05:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami, come to the store and pick one with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.75,0:05:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I need to take Meat\Nto her checkup today.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.83,0:05:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Meat?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.04,0:05:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! She's a white, fluffy, squishy and lovable creature!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.71,0:05:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If I leave her alone, she'll die of loneliness,\Nso I need to be with her.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.29,0:05:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the same way, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.83,0:05:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No means no.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.79,0:05:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a bad idea to venture out\Nby yourself for a change.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.25,0:05:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so heartless, Kagami.\NA rabbit and I are on the same level?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.83,0:06:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Sasami? Shopping?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.67,0:06:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.46,0:06:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you buying?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.79,0:06:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um, a bicycle.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.21,0:06:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. To ride to school...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.38,0:06:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get one with a basket like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.42,0:06:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.00,0:06:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A proper Tsukuyomi Priestess has no need for cuteness.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.96,0:06:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The desire to seek comfort and relief in physical objects\Nturns into weakness and lowers your defenses.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.54,0:06:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotions of right and wrong also cloud one's judgment\Nwhen running the world righteously.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.08,0:06:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have many memories about my mother,\Nbut what I do have I remember vividly.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.54,0:06:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How I learned my techniques from her\Nand practiced with her.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.92,0:07:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always with my mother when I was little.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.08,0:07:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Sasami?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.88,0:07:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.33,0:07:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this annoying flashing object?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.54,0:07:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this? You control these buttons\Nand move the crane.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.62,0:07:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you catch stuffed dolls with it. Do you want to try it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.29,0:07:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Puppets are evil.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.00,0:07:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy to insert a soul into\Nthose that look like a child in particular.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.75,0:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're cursed items set up by the enemy.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.88,0:07:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!\NThey're cursed items set up by the enemy.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.42,0:07:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen to me when I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.25,0:07:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn! It's hard...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.83,0:07:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let your mother handle it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.58,0:07:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.92,0:07:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A proper Tsukuyomi priestess prefers expedience.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.88,0:07:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's against the rules!\NThe store clerks are staring at us!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.46,0:07:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm going to enspell the doll and make it move.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.17,0:07:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Creepy!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.25,0:08:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It fell.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.29,0:08:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to get it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I give you permission.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A Tsukuyomi priestess' permission is that of the gods'-
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.75,0:08:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! The store clerks are coming this way!\NA Tsukuyomi priestess' permission is that of the gods'-
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.62,0:08:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Mother!\NA Tsukuyomi priestess' permission is that of the gods'-
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.42,0:08:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take off all of a sudden!\NI'm not good in physical matters!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.92,0:08:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was born sickly, so she often stayed in bed.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.75,0:08:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to take care of her a lot, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.92,0:08:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! We almost got arrested for that!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.00,0:08:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This Tsukuyomi priestess can't be intimidated\Nby law enforcement so easily.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.83,0:08:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother needs to take a break.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.08,0:08:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, you're physically weaker than me.\NThat's a real problem as a human.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.75,0:08:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see no benefit in physical ability!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.42,0:08:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait here for a second.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.50,0:08:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel something unsettling coming from it. What is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.29,0:08:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice cream. It's a type of cold sweets.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.25,0:08:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Consuming articles of taste is evil. Any pleasure is-
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.92,0:08:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just have it. Here.\NConsuming articles of taste is evil. Any pleasure is-
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.54,0:09:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.38,0:09:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, my mother just made a cute noise!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.33,0:09:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother is always cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.83,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, do you have a computer?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.62,0:09:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's convenient to have one.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.25,0:09:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A proper Tsukuyomi priestess\Nfinds no value in convenience.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, buy me this!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.46,0:09:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll not. Material desire is evil.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.50,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But my Big Brother would have\Nno problem buying it for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's out of the question.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.79,0:09:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't rely on him. Your mind will rot.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.33,0:09:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pick clothes for you. I bet you get tired\Nof wearing the priestess' uniform all the time.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.88,0:09:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a priestess so wearing the\Npriestess' vestment is natural to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.17,0:09:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no need for worldly clothes.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.88,0:09:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.92,0:09:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, do you have more time?\NCan we eat dinner together?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.83,0:09:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to be a helpless little child,\Nbut now listen to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.04,0:09:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you want to eat?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.29,0:10:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.75,0:10:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, Sasami,\NI need to talk to you about something-
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.71,0:10:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Italian? I bet you've never had it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.83,0:10:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sasami. I said wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.17,0:10:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I still harbor those memories of my\Nmother every now and then.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.33,0:10:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! There are so many animals!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.96,0:10:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many fluffy things! Is this Heaven or what?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.21,0:10:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Meat! This is the doctor's office.\NIt's not going to be scary, so you can be calm.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.29,0:10:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! To think you'd treat a bunny like a baby,\Nyou know what you're doing, huh, Kagami?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.29,0:10:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my sister!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.71,0:10:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're irritating. You should go die already.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.42,0:10:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That fluffy thing is wearing clothes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.79,0:10:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to be a sign from Heaven\Nthat I should cuddle with Meat!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.50,0:10:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Meat! What do you think about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.54,0:10:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not going anywhere for a while...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.46,0:11:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasami...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.83,0:11:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.17,0:11:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who feeds you here?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually my big brother does.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.88,0:11:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It's easy, so watch me. Like this...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.58,0:11:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, Sasami, I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.62,0:11:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.92,0:11:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.58,0:11:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You said earlier that you had fun, remember?\NSasami, that's what a mother would want for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.83,0:11:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, we'd never\Nshared time as parent and child before;
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.04,0:11:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,shopping or talking about things and such.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.83,0:11:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a poor mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Sasami.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.88,0:11:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't apologize, Mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.08,0:12:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just happy that we're able to spend time together,\Neven if just for a little while.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.42,0:12:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing stuff like this has been my dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I made you sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.21,0:12:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay; I always knew that you were trying your best\Nto raise me to be a good successor
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.42,0:12:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,when you were always busy with your duty.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.00,0:12:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasami...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.50,0:12:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I really mean it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.62,0:12:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.00,0:12:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And because of that I have something I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.00,0:12:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.75,0:12:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.08,0:12:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you're...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.92,0:12:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,already...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.58,0:12:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...dead.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.75,0:13:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dead, you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.29,0:13:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasami...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.88,0:13:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...you thought that I didn't know that?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.92,0:13:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.38,0:13:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm dead.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.67,0:13:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, so that means...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.96,0:13:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I may look decent because of the Alteration,\Nbut my body is actually a corpse.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.50,0:13:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's definitely decaying, but the people\Naround me simply can't tell.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.96,0:13:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my true form.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.83,0:13:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone dies.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.29,0:13:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The souls of the dead slide down the slope\Nto the spirit realms and head to the Underworld.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.42,0:13:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no reincarnation. There is no resurrection, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.21,0:13:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the rule.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.96,0:13:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there is a way out.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.75,0:14:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I ate of the fruit of Yomi, the Land of the Dead,\Nin other words, before I joined the world of the Dead,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.54,0:14:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I negotiated with the King of Underworld.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.42,0:14:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Our interests were the same,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.67,0:14:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so he let me return to this world\Nuntil my body rots away completely.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.79,0:14:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Resurrection is such a horrid thing,\Neven the God of Creation failed!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.08,0:14:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know why, Sasami?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.29,0:14:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was ready to depart; I was satisfied.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.04,0:14:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I saw how you were living your life of leisure,\Nhaving run away from the shrine,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.50,0:14:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,abandoning your duty as a Tsukuyomi Priestess!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.33,0:14:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to stay dead anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.29,0:14:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I asked you to take care of this world.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.88,0:14:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You nodded and even said\N"You can count on me, Mother."
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But you broke your promise.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.00,0:15:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll not blame you for that because\Nyou're not the only one who sinned.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.79,0:15:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was also my sin for passing before all the effort\Nof your training bore fruit... before you matured...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.58,0:15:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to Tsukuyomi Shrine, Sasami.\NThere you can train again.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.71,0:15:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The shrine's been destroyed.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.00,0:15:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.88,0:15:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The physical building isn't what's important.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.38,0:15:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It is sufficient that you have a place where\Nyou can train quietly, away from this ridiculous world.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.50,0:15:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.42,0:15:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.92,0:15:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going back!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.79,0:15:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What point is there in maintaining a world\Nso convenient for humans
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.75,0:15:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,while you struggle so much?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.58,0:15:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a priestess of the Tsukuyomi!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.54,0:15:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea, Sasami.\NNo one is asking you how YOU feel here.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.79,0:15:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for Humanity!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.83,0:15:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean to tell me your happiness,\Nfreedom and pleasure
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.67,0:15:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,are worth more than the future of Humankind?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.96,0:16:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life isn't the only one borne on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.33,0:16:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not just your world. It's more enormous and noble!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.38,0:16:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So stop being so selfish!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.50,0:16:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.71,0:16:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being a baby, you fool!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.62,0:16:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Grow up already!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.96,0:16:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your existence is worthless\Nif you're not a Tsukuyomi priestess!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.79,0:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Living your life aimlessly, neglecting your duty\Nand idling your time away is practically a crime!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you understand that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.92,0:16:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Pampering you so much was a grave mistake,\Nyou good-for-nothing daughter!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.00,0:16:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't get too excited now, Mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.21,0:16:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a parent-teacher-student meeting, Mother?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.79,0:16:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsurugi...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.04,0:16:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd heard about it, but this is my first time\Nactually seeing it...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.21,0:16:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...a person resurrected from the Underworld.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.62,0:16:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop speaking like a human.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.62,0:16:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but an evil god.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.25,0:16:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you talk Sasami into this?\NWith your smile and sweet words?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.58,0:17:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no evil god! YOU'RE the monster\Nwho came back from death!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.21,0:17:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No human; not even a god should return from the dead!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.88,0:17:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a rule of this world set by the Old Man himself!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.88,0:17:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because life is finite that\Nyou can live your life without regret.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.62,0:17:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I admit that I'm a lazy god who's abandoned the duty\Nto manage this world myself,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.08,0:17:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't ignore a serious violation of the rules like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.79,0:17:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm gonna fix that!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.42,0:17:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No one talked Sasami into it!\NShe chose on her own to live her life.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.88,0:17:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You died and left her alone all this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.92,0:17:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for you to act like her mother now!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.71,0:17:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your ass on the super express\Nback to the Underworld!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.96,0:17:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She underestimates me, does she?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.75,0:17:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Tsukuyomi priestess, the pinnacle of the\NTsukuyomi Shrine, who can exorcise any apparition!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Banishing evil gods is our specialty!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.62,0:17:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no evil god!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.71,0:18:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as the myth says, you're no good at fighting,\Nare you, Sun God?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.12,0:18:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsurugi!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.12,0:18:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.79,0:18:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sister Tsurugi!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.75,0:18:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.75,0:18:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's strong! You two are no match for her!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.25,0:18:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you stop taking it all on yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.62,0:18:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember you're an empty shell\Nthat can't exert your true power.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.46,0:18:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.83,0:18:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not speaking out against an abusive parent\Nis a teacher's disgrace.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.04,0:18:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You lot are a bunch of nonchalant people.\NThe gods of this country are too laidback.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.08,0:18:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to leave this country to the likes of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.42,0:18:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Progress and prosperity of this world\Nrequires that it is managed by humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.54,0:18:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All is for the world and for Humanity.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.33,0:18:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Educating Sasami and making sure that she serves as a\NTsukuyomi priestess are the last duties I must carry out.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.42,0:18:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no grudge against you,\Nbut if you attempt to interfere...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.33,0:18:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...death will come to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.88,0:19:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to the Underworld!\NThere's someone I don't like down there!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.08,0:19:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.21,0:19:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect nothing less from the Divine Sword\NAme no Murakumo.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.88,0:19:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What an impressive force.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.58,0:19:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the end of the day,\Nit's nothing but a defensive sword.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.67,0:19:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A grass cutter, used solely for defense,\Nsimply lacks the malice required to defeat others!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that's...!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.83,0:19:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It once defeated the serpent Yamata no Orochi\Nand fell broken to its curse,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.25,0:19:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's since been sharpened in the afterworld...\NThe Dark Sword, Ame no Habakiri!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.62,0:19:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the god-slaying demon sword,\Nwhich I received from the King of the Underworld.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.17,0:19:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame no Habakiri and the Underworld?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I get it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.29,0:19:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you were way too powerful for a human,\Nbut now it all makes sense!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.88,0:19:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn mama's boy... How dare he...!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.25,0:19:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sister! Why you...!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.29,0:19:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.33,0:19:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even touch me with your level of divinity.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.96,0:20:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I bear the demon sword blessed by\Nthe King of the Underworld!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.50,0:20:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Big sister Kagami!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.92,0:20:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.92,0:20:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU...!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.25,0:20:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You are too weak!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.67,0:20:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The path to the Underworld opens easily for me\Nsince I came back from the Land of the Dead.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.67,0:20:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you descend the slope to the land of the dead,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.46,0:20:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,it is impossible to turn back, even for a god.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.50,0:20:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your era ended long ago, Sun Goddess.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.04,0:20:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall... and let the Moon have the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.17,0:20:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.96,0:20:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Move, little bug.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.33,0:21:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're acting like some kind of allies of justice,\Nthinking you're protecting my spoiled daughter,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.46,0:21:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's completely meaningless! Worthless!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For the world and for Humanity,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.58,0:21:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasami is obligated to become a great priestess\Nand lead this country righteously.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.50,0:21:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama's dumb and doesn't get it...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.04,0:21:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But why do you do all this ugly stuff?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.08,0:21:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We were all happy before you came!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.62,0:21:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sister Tsurugi seemed really happy!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.96,0:21:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sister Kagami started to smile more than before!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.75,0:21:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All because of Mama-lin!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.71,0:21:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't understand what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.50,0:21:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama doesn't get it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.04,0:21:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let me put it simply for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.21,0:21:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You are in my way.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.54,0:21:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.92,0:21:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it already! Okay, I'm going back!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.04,0:21:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to the shrine!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.58,0:21:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a Tsukuyomi priestess again, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.29,0:22:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back to the human world.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.71,0:22:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's time for the ending theme again!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.88,0:22:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, at last, I promise I'll share Sasami's lovely voice\Nwith all you out there in your living rooms!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.79,0:22:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But actually it doesn't look like that's going to happen...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.58,0:22:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what should I do now?\NDo I have to sing it again for her?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.38,0:22:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:42.71,0:22:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect timing, Mother!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.92,0:22:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:46.42,0:22:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:47.50,0:22:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, hold this microphone. Are you ready now?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.54,0:22:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now sing! Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:51.92,0:22:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, I have no idea what's going on here!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:55.21,0:22:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all I don't sing!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.83,0:22:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A proper Tsukuyomi priestess has no need to sing!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:58.54,0:23:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:00.79,0:23:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Since this episode was pretty serious,\Nwe just wanted to end it cheerfully with this song.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.00,0:23:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're recording it, but I doubt\Nthat it's going to be used again.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.96,0:23:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But please go ahead and sing, just in case.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.33,0:23:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Inhale!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.96,0:23:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dokomade mo... hibiku... s-s-sy... symphony\NThat's a... s-s-sy... symphony that echoes... far away
Dialogue: 10,0:23:21.17,0:23:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...sasu koi ir-\N...shines on the love-
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.83,0:23:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not fooling me!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.96,0:23:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to do stuff like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:29.71,0:23:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamiomi, sit still! I'll punish you!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.83,0:23:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Don't hit me with the microphone, Mother!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.50,0:23:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to use that every time!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:39.08,0:23:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll see you next time!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:48.79,0:23:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's time for Ganbaranai Exercise!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.38,0:23:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,First inhale!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:52.92,0:23:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretend you're inhaling Sasami's scent\Nall the way into your lungs!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:55.75,0:23:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now one, two!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:58.17,0:23:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Two, two!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.08,0:24:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, open your arms wide!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.33,0:24:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretend you're holding Sasami!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:04.21,0:24:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now one, two, Sasami!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.46,0:24:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Two, two, I love you!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:08.21,0:24:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's have a wonderful day today!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.58,0:24:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, Episode 7:\N"I Forgot How To Speak"
